instance standardization : DTDFVocab:Standardization [
    base:desc "The document references industry standards such as SysML for Model-Based Systems Engineering, ACME, AADL, MontiArc as architecture description languages for component & connector perspectives, and methodologies like RFLP, OOSEM, SPES, SMArDT for system complexity handling. These standards are applicable to Digital Twin development processes."
]